WellPoint Inc. (WLP) , the largest U.S.
health insurer by enrollment, will raise the amount of money
participating doctors receive in an effort to improve the
quality of care.  The program also will aim to enhance information sharing
and provide support from WellPoint clinical workers, the
Indianapolis-based company said in a statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
